hadiths[201]{hadithnumber,text}:
5385,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Zaid bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar Siddeeq se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs chandi ke bartan mein peeta hai wo apne pet mein ghataaghat jahannam ki aag bhar raha hai."
5386,"Quteba aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne hamein Lais-bin-Sad se yahi hadis bayan ki. yahi hadis mujhey Ali-bin Hujr Sadi ne bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ismail bin-Ulaih ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, aur hamein ibne-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muhammad Bishr ne hadis sunai Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hadis bayan ki, abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Waleed bin shujaa ne kaha : hamein Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne Ubaidullah se hadis bayan ki Muhammad-bin abi-Bakr muqaddami ne kaha : hamein Fuzel bin Sulaiman ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Musa-bin-Aqba ne hadis sunai. Sheban-bin-Farukh ne kaha : hamein Jareer-bin-Haazim ne Abdur-Rehman siraaj se un sab (Lais-bin-Sad Ayub Muhammad-bin-Bishr Yahya-bin-Saeed Ubaidullah Musa-bin-Aqba aur Abdur-Rehman siraaj) ne Naafe se imam Malik-bin-Anas ki hadis ki tarah aur Naafe se ( uper ( unhi ki sanad ke sath riwayat bayan ki aur Ubaidullah se Ali-bin-Mus-hir ki riwayat mein izafa kya : bila shubah jo shakhs chandi ya soney ke bartan mein khata ya peeta hai. unmein se aur kisi ki hadis mein khaney aur soney (ke bartan (ka zikr nahi. sirf ibne-mus-hir ki hadis mein hai."
5387,"Usman bin Murra ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman ne apni khala Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs soney ya chandi ke bartan mein peeta hai wo apne pet mein ghataaghat jahannam ki aag bhar raha hai."
5388,"(abu khaisma) Zuhair ne kaha : hamein Ashas ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Muawiya bin Suwed bin Muqrin ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) chizon ka hukm diya hai aur saat (7) chizon se roka mareez ki iyaadat karne, janazey ke sath Sharik hone, chheenk ka jawab dene (apni) qism ya qism dene waley (ki qasam) poori karne, mazloom ki madad karne, dawat qabool karne, aur angoothiyon se, ya soney ki anguthi pahnney se, chandi ke bartan main ( khaney ( peeney arghawani (surkh) gaddon se (agar wo resham ke hon) mus-hir ke ilaaqey qas ke baney huey kapdon (jo resham ke hotey they.) aur (kisi bhi qism ke) resham istibraq aur deebaaj ko pahnney se roka (istibraq resham ka mota kapda tha aur deebaaj baareek.)"
5389,"abu-Awana ne hamein Ashas bin Sulaim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis sunai, siwaey apni qism ya qism dene waley (ki qism (ke alfaz ke , unhon-ne hadis mein ye fiqra nahi kaha : aur uske bajaey gumshuda cheez ka elaan karne ka zikr kya."
5390,Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur Jarir donon ne Shebani se unhon-ne Ashas bin abi Shasa se isi sanad ke sath Zuhair ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur baghair shak ke qism dene waley (ki qasam) poori karne ke alfaz kahey aur hadis mein mazeed bayan kya : aur chandi (ke bartan) mein peeney se (mana kya) kyonke jo shakhs duniya mein usmein piyega. wo aakhirat mein usmein nahi piyega.
5391,ibne-Idrees ne kaha : hamein Abu-Ishaq Shebani aur Lais bin abi Saleem ne Ashas bin abi Shasa se un sab ki sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Jarir aur ibne-Mus-hir ke izaafey ka zikr nahi kya.
5392,"Shoba ne Ashas bin Sulaim se un sab ki sanad ke sath unki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki, siwaey unke riwayat ki hui alfaz : salam aam karne ke bajaey kaha : aur salam ka jawab dene aur kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein soney ki anguthi ya soney ke kadey se mana farmaya."
5393,hamein Sufiyan ne Ashas bin abi Shasa se un sab ki sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur shak ke baghair salam aam karne aur soney ki anguthi kaha.
5394,"Saeed bin-Amr bin Sehal bin Ishaq bin Muhammad-bin Ashas bin Qais ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine unhein abu farwa se zikr kartey huey suna ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : ham (Iran ki pichhli daarul-hukoomat ( madaain mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani maanga to aik zameendaar chandi ke bartan mein mashroob ley aaya, Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ( mashroob (ke samet wo bartan phenk diya aur kaha : main tum logon ko bata raha hun ke main pahley us se keh chuka hun ke wo mujhey us (chandi ke bartan) mein na pilaaey kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai. soney aur chandi ke bartan mein na piyo aur deebaaj aur hareer na pahno kyonke ye cheezein duniya mein un (kafiron) ke liye hain aur aakhirat mein qiyamat ke din tumharey liye hain."
5395,"ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein yahi hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu farwa Johni se hadis sunai, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they. ham Madaain mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they phir uski tarah bayan kya aur us hadis mein qiyamat ke din (ke alfaz ( zikr nahi kiye."
5396,"ibne-abi Najeeh ne pehley hamein Mujahid se, unhon-ne ibne-abi-Lela se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. phir hamein Yazeed ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ye hadis ibne-abi-Lela se suni , unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se, phir hamein abu farwa ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine ibne-Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) se suni aur mera khayal ye hai ke ibne-abi-Lela ne bhi ye hadis ibne- Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) se suni, unhon-ne kaha : ham Madaain mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath ( unke dastey mein) they. phir usi ki tarah bayan kya aur qiyamat ke din ke alfaz nahi kahey."
5397,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine dekha ke Madaain mein Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani maanga to aik shakhs unke paas chandi ka bartan lekar aaya phir unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se ibne-Akeem (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat ki tarah bayan kya."
5398,"Wakee Muhammad-bin-Jafar ibne-abi Adi aur Behaz , un sab ne Shoba se Muaz ki hadis ki tarah unhi ki sanad ke sath hadis riwayat ki aur akeley Muaz ke siwa, unmein se kisi ne hadis mein maine Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke alfaz nahi kahey. sab ne yahi kya : Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani maanga."
5399,"Mansoor aur Ibne-Aun donon ne Mujahid se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un logon ki riwayat ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki jinka ham ne zikr kya hai."
5400,"Saif ne kaha ke maine Mujahid ko kehtey huey suna, maine Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se suna, Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani maanga to aik majusi unke paas chandi ke bartan mein pani laya to unhon (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey hoey suna hai. na resham pehno na deebaaj pahno aur na soney aur chandi ke bartan mein piyo aur na un (qeemtii dhaaton) ki rakaabiyon ( pleton ( mein kha kyonki ye bartan duniya mein un (kuffaar (ke liye hain."
5401,"Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne masjid ke darwazey ke qareeb (baazaar mein) aik reshami hulla (eik jaisi reshmi chaadaron ka joda baktey huey) dekha. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! kitna achchha ho agar aap ye hulla khareed lein aur Juma ke din logon ke samney ( khutba dene ke liye) aur jab koi wafad aap ke paas aaey to usey zeb tan farmaein (pehnein)! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usko ( duniya mein) sirf wo log pahntey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas unmein se kuchh reshami hulley aaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik hulla Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ata farmaya, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap ne mujhey ye hulla pahnney ke liye diya hai halanke aap ne utaarid (bin haajib bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) jo masjid ke darwazey ke bahar hulley bech rahe they) ke hulley ke barey mein jo farmaya tha? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine ye hulla tum ko pehnney ke liye nahi diya. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo hulla Makka main apne aik bhai ko de diya jo mushrik tha."
5402,"Ubaidullah aur Musa-bin-Aqba donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5403,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha : hamein Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke utaarid tamimi bazar mein aik reshami hulla (bechney ke liye) uski qeemat bata raha hai. ye baadshaahon ke paas jaya karta tha aur unse inaam w ikraam wsool karta tha, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine utaarid ko dekha hai wo bazar mein aik reshami hulla bech raha hai, aap usey khareed letey to aap Arab ke wufood aatey (is waqt) aap usko zeb tan farmatey aur mera khayal hai (ye bhi) kaha : aur Juma ke din bhi aap usey zeb tan farmatey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : duniya mein resham sirf wahi shakhs pehnta hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi hota. is waqiey ke baad (ka aik din aaya to ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kai reshami hulley aaey aap ne aik hulla Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhi bheja , aik Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja aur aik hulla Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya aur farmaya : usko phaad kar apni aurton ko dupattey bana do. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) apne hulley ko utha kar laey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ne ye hulla mere paas bheja hai halanke aap ne kal hi utaarid ke hulley ke mutaalliq farmaya tha. jo aap ne farmaya tha? aap ne farmaya : maine tumharey paas ye hulla isliye nahi bheja ke usey tum khud pahno , balke maine tumharey paas ye isliye bheja hai ke tum kuchh ( fayda ( hasil karo. to rahe Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) to wo apna hulla pahan kar aa gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko is tarah dekha jis se unhein pata chal gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unka aisa karna pasand nahi aaya unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap mujhey is tarah kyon dekh rahe hain? aap hi ne to usey mere paas bheja tha. aap ne farmaya : maine tumharey paas isliye nahi bheja tha ke tum khud usko pahan lo. balke maine isliye us hulley ko tumharey paas bheja tha ke tum usko phaad kar apni aurton mein dupattey bana do."
5404,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne istibraq ( motey resham (ka aik hulla bazar mein farokht hota hua dekha unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! usey khareed lijiye aur eid aur wufood ki aamad par usey zeb tan farmaiye to rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye sirf aisey shakhs ka libaas hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. kaha : phir jab tak Allah ko manzoor tha waqt guzra ( lafzi tarjama : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) usi haalat mein rahe ( phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke paas deebaaj ka aik jubba bhej diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) usko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ne farmaya tha : ye us shakhs ka libaas hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. ya aap ne (is tarah) farmaya tha : usko wo shakhs pehnta hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. phir aap ne yahi mere paas bhej diya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (is liye ke) tum usko farokht kar do aur us (ki qeemat ( se apni zarurat poori kar lo."
5405,Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
5406,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Abu-Bakar bin Hafs ne Salim se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne utaarid ke khandan walon mein se aik aadmi (ke kandhon ( par deebaaj ya resham ki aik Quba dekhi to unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : kitna achchha ho agar aap usko khareed lein ! aap ne farmaya : usko sirf wo shakhs pehnta hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. phir ( baad mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik reshami hulla hadiya kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo hulla mere paas bhej diya, kaha : maine kaha : aap ne wo hulla mere paas bhej diya hai. jabke main iske mutaalliq aap se sun chuka hon, aap ne iske barey mein jo farmaya tha so farmaya tha? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine usey tumharey paas sirf isliye bheja hai ke tum us se fayda uthaao."
5407,"Rooh ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abu-Bakar bin Hafs ne Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bin-Khattab ne aale-Utaarid ke aik aadmi (ke kandhon ( par (bechney ke liye aik hulla) dekha, jis tarah Yahya-bin-Saeed ki aik hadis hai. magar unhon-ne ye alfaz kahey : maine usey tumharey paas sirf isliye bheja tha ke tum us se fayda uthao aur isliye tumharey paas nahi bheja tha ke tum (khud) usey pehno."
5408,"Yahya bin abi Ishaq ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne mujh se istibraq ke mutaalliq malum kya, kaha : maine kaha : wo deebaaj jo mota aur sakht ho. unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik shakhs (ke kandhey ( par istibraq ka aik hulla dekha, wo us ( hulley ( ko lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey, phir unhon-ne un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, albatta usmein ye kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine ye jubba isliye tumharey paas bheja ke tum iske zariey se (usey bech kar) kuchh maal hasil kar lo."
5409,"Hazrat Asma binte- Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Abdullah (kaisaan) se riwayat hai, jo ke Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ka Maula aur Ata ke ladkey ka maamun tha, ne kaha ke mujhey Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja aur kehlaaya ke maine suna hai ke tum teen chizon ko haram kehtey ho, aik to kapdey ko jis mein reshami naqsh hon, doosrey Urjuwani (yani surkh) zeen posh ko aur teesrey tamam rajab ke mahiney mein rozey rakhney ko, to saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke rajab ke mahiney ke rozon ko kon haram kahega ? jo shakhs hamesha roza rakhega ( saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hamesha roza ilawa dono eidon aur dinon tashreeq ke rakhtey they aur unka mazhab yahi hai ke saume-dahar makruh nahi hai) aur kapdey ke reshami nuqoosh ka tu ney zikr kya hai to maine saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke hareer ( resham ( wo pahnega jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi, to mujhey dar hua ke kahin naqshi kapda bhi hareer ( resham ( na ho aur urjuwani zeen posh , to khud Abdullah ka zeen posh urjuwani hai. ye sab maine ja kar Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) se kaha to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye jubba maujood hai, phir unhon-ne Tiyalisi kasarwaani jubba (jo Iraan ke badshah Kisraa ki taraf mansub tha) nikala jiske garebaan par resham laga hua tha aur daman bhi reshami they. Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke ye jubba Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ki wafat tak unke paas tha. jab wo faut ho gain to ye jubba maine ley liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko pehna kartey they ab ham usko dho kar uska pani beemaaron ko shifa ke liye pilaatey hain."
5410,"Shoba ne khaleefa bin Kab abi Zibyan se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo khutba detey huey keh rahe they : suno ! apni aurton ko resham na pahnaao kyonke maine Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bin-Khattab ko (ye hadis bayan kartey huey) suna hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : resham na pahno, kyonke jisne duniya mein usey pehna wo aakhirat mein usko nahi pahnega."
5411,"Ahmed bin-Abdullah-bin Yunus ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zuhair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aasim ahwal ne abu-Usman se hadis bayan ki, kaha : jab ham aazarbaijan mein they, to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamari taraf ( khat mein) likh bheja : Utba-bin- Farqad ! tumharey paas jo maal hai wo na tumhari kamaai se hai, na tumharey maan-baap ki kamaai se, musalmanon ko unki rihaaishgaahon mein wahi khana pet bharkey khilaao jis se apni rihaaishgaah main tum khud pet bhartey ho aur tum log aish w ishrat se mushrekeen ke libaas aur resham ke pahnaawon se door rehna, kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne resham ke pahnaawey se mana farmaya hai, magar itna (jaaiz hai), (ye farma kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni 2 ungliyan, darmyani ungli aur shahadat ki ungli milaaein aur unhein hamarey samney buland farmaya, Zuhair ne kaha : Aasim ne kaha : ye us khat mein hai, (ibne-Younus ne) kaha : aur Zuhair ne (bhi) apni 2 ungliyan uthaain."
5412,Jarir bin abdul-hameed aur Hafs bin Ghiyas donon ne Aasim se isi sanad ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se resham ke barey mein isi tarah riwayat ki.
5413,"Jarir ne Sulaiman Taimi se, unhon-ne abu-Usmaan se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Utba-bin- Farqad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they, to hamarey paas Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka maktoob aaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : resham (ka libaas) uske siwa koi shakhs nahi pehnta jiska aakhirat mein usmein se koi hissey na ho, siwaey itney (resham) ke (itni miqdar jaaiz hai) abu-Usman ne angoothey ke sath ki apni 2 ungliyon se ishara kya. mujhey is tarah malum hua ke jaisey wo tailsaan ( nishanat wali abaa (ke batanon wali jagah (ke barabar) ho, yahan tak ke maine (asl) telsaan dekhey, (wo itni miqdar hi thi.)"
5414,"Motamir ne apne walid (Sulaiman Taimi) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Usmaan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham Utba-bin-Farqad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they, Jarir ki hadis ki tarah."
5415,"Shoba ne Qatada se riwayat ki, kaha : maine abu-Usman nehdi se suna, kaha : hamarey paas Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka maktoob aaya, us waqt ham aazarbaaijan mein Utba-bin- Farqad (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they ya Sham (Syria) mein they, usmein ye likha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itni miqdar yani 2 ungliyon se zyada resham pahnney se mana kya hai. abu-Usman ne kaha : ham ne ye samajhney mein zara twaqquf na kya ke unki murad naqsh w nigaar se hai (jo kinaron par hotey hain.)"
5416,"Hisham ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath, usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur abu-Usmaan ka qaul zikr nahi kya."
5417,"Muaz ke walid Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Aamir Shabi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Suwed bin ghafala (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne jaabiya mein khutba diya aur kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne resham pahnney se mana farmaya, siwaey 2 ya teen ya char ungliyon (ki patti) ke."
5418,Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5419,"abu-Zubair ne kaha ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din deebaaj ki Quba pahni jo aapko hadiya ki gaee thi, phir fauran hi aap ne usko utaar diya aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhej di. aap se kaha gaya : ya Rasulullah! aap ne usko fauran utaar diya hai. aap ne farmaya : mujhey Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne us se mana kar diya. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huey aaey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap ne aik cheez na-pasand ki aur wo mujhey de di ! ab mere liye kya (rasta) hai? aap ne farmaya : maine ye tumhen pahnney ke liye nahi di, maine tumhen isliye di ke usko bech lo. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko 2 hazar dirham mein farokht kar diya."
5420,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu Aun se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Abu-Saleh se suna, wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis suna rahe they, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik reshami hulla hadiya kya gaya, aap ne wo mere paas bhej diya, maine usko pehan liya, phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par ghussa mehsus kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine ye tumharey paas isliye nahi bheja tha ke tum usko pahan lo, maine tumharey paas isliye bheja tha ke tum usko kaat kar aurton mein dupattey baant do."
5421,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar, donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu Aun se isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai. Muaz ki bayan ki hui hadis mein hai : aap ne mujhey hukm diya to maine kaat kar (apne ghar ki) aurton mein baant diya aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki hadis mein hai : maine usko kaat kar (apne ghar ki) aurton mein baant diya aur unhon-ne aap ne mujhey hukm diya (ke alfaz) zikr nahi kiye."
5422,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, abu-Kuraib aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hamein hadis bayan ki. alfaz Zuhair ke hain. kaha : hamein Wakee ne Misar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Aun Saqafi se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh hanfi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke daumatul-jandal ke (hukmaraan ( Akeedar ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein resham ka aik kapda hadiya bheja, aap ne wo kapda Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya aur farmaya : usko kaat kar (teenon) faatimaaon ( Fatima binte-rasoolullaah (sl), Fatima binte- Asad , yani Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida, aur Fatima binte- Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) mein odhniyaan baant 2 Abu-Bakar aur abu-Kuraib ne (faatimaaon ke darmiyan ke bajaey) aurton ke darmiyan kaha."
5423,"Zaid-bin Wahab ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik reshami hulla diya, main usey pehan kar nikla to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par ghussa dekha, kaha : phir maine usko phaad kar apne ghar ki aurton mein taqseem kar diya."
5424,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Sundus (baareek resham (ka aik jubba bheja, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ne mere paas ye jubba bheja hai. halanke aap ne iske mutaalliq (pahley) jo farmaya tha wo farma chukey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine ye tumharey paas isliye nahi bheja ke tum usko pehno, maine tumharey paas isliye bheja hai ke tum uski qeemat se fayda uthaao."
5425,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne duniya mein resham pehna wo aakhirat mein usko nahi pahnega.
5426,Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne duniya mein resham pehna wo aakhirat mein usko nahi pahnega.
5427,"Leis ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne abul-khair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko resham ki aik khuli Quba hadiye mein di gaee, aap ne wo pahni aur Namaz padhi, phir usko kheench kar utaar diya, jaisey aap usey na-pasand kar rahe hon, phir farmaya : ye (aba) taqwa ikhtiyar karne walon ke liye munasib nahi hai."
5428,abdul-Hameed ne Jafar se kaha : mujhey Yazeed bin abi Habib ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
5429,"abu-Usama ne hamein Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Qatada ne hamein hadis sunai ke Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Hazrat Zubair-bin-Awam (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik safar mein khaarish ki bina par ya kisi aur takleef ki bina par jo unhein laahiq ho gaee thi. resham pahnney ki ijazat marahmat farmai. (halaat mein yahi madaawa muyassar tha.)"
5430,Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Saeed ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur safar mein ka zikr nahi kya.
5431,"Wakee ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko unhein laahiq honey wali khaarish ki wjah se resham pahnney ki ijazat di."
5432,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5433,Hammam ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis sunai ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Hazrat Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juon (ki khaarish) ki shikayat ki to aap ne un donon ko unhein pesh aaney wali jang ke doran mein resham pahnney ki ijazat de di.
5434,"Muaz bin Hisham ne hamein bayan kya, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Yahya (bin abi kaseer) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Muhammad-bin Ibrahim bin-Haaris ne hadis sunai ke ibne-Madaan ne unhein bataya ke unhein Jubair-bin-Nufair ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey gerwey rang ke 2 kapdey pahney huey dekha to aap ne farmaya : ye ka firon ke kapdey hain tum unhein mat pehno."
5435,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne khabar di Wakee ne Ali bin-Mubarak se bayan kya, Hisham aur Ali bin-Mubarak donon ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, donon ne (ibne-Madaan ke bajaey) Khalid-bin Madaan kaha."
5436,"Taaus ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey gerwey rang ke 2 kapdey pahney huey dekha to aap ne farmaya : kya tumhari maan ne tumhen ye kapdey pahnney ka hukm diya hai? maine kaha : main unko dho daalun? aap ne farmaya : balke unko jala do."
5437,"Naafe ne Ibrahim bin-Abdullah Hunain se unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qas (ilaaqey) ke baney huey (reshami kapdey) aur gerwey rang ke kapdey pahnney se, soney ki anguthi pahnney se aur rukoo mein Quran Majeed padhney se mana farmaya."
5438,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Hunain ne hadis bayan ki unke walid ne unhein hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jab main rukoo kar raha hun. Quran Majeed padhney se aur (umumi haalat mein) sona aur gerwey rang ka libaas pahnney se mana farmaya."
5439,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin-Abdullah Hunain se unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey soney ki anguthi pahnney se resham ke kapdey pahnney se rukoo aur sujood mein Quran Majeed padhney se aur gerwey rang ka libaas pahnney se mana farmaya."
5440,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kis qism ka libas zyada mahboob tha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada achchha lagta tha? unhon-ne kaha : dhari daar (yamni) chadar."
5441,"Hisham ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kapdon mein sabse zyada pasand dhaari daar (yamni chadar thi.)"
5442,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne kaha : hamein Humaid ne abu-Burda se hadis sunai, kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne aik mota tehband jo Yaman mein banaya jata hai aur aik uper ki chadar (moti sakht aur pewand lagey hone ki wjah se) jisey ( مُلَبَّدَہ ( kaha jata hai nikal kar dikhai, kaha : unhon-ne Allah ki qism khaai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhi 2 kapdon mein daai ajal ko labbaik kaha tha."
5443,"Ali-bin Hujr Sadi Muhammad-bin-Hatim aur Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne (Ismail) ibne-Ulaih se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Humaid bin Hilal se, unhon-ne abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hamein aik tehband aur aik pewand lagi hui moti chadar nikal kar dikhai aur farmaya : unhi 2 kapdon main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui thi. ibne- Hatim ne apni hadis mein kaha : mota tehband."
5444,Mamar ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur kaha : mota tehband.
5445,"Safiya-binte-Sheba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik subah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah bahar nikley ke aap ke jism par aik moti murabba lakeeron wali kaley baalon se bani hui chadar thi. (aam si, khurdari aur kam qeemat chadar.)"
5446,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka takiya jiske sath aap tek lagaatey they chamdey ka bana hua tha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi."
5447,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka bistar ( gaddaa ( jis par aap sotey they, chamdey ka tha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi."
5448,ibne-Numair aur abu-Muawiya donon ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath khabar di aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka soney ka bichhona aur abu-Muawiya ki hadis mein hai. jis par aap sotey they.
5449,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed, Amr Naaqid aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne ibne-Munkadir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab maine shadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : kya tum ne bichhonon ke ghilaf banaey hain? maine arz ki, hamarey paas ghilaaf kahan se aaey? aap ne farmaya : ab an-qareeb hongey."
5450,"Wakee ne hamein Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Munkadir se unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab maine shadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : kya tum ne bichhonon ke ghilaaf banaey hain? maine arz ki, hamarey paas ghilaaf kahan se aaey? aap ne farmaya : ab an-qareeb ho jaengey. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : meri biwi ke paas aik ghilaaf tha main us se kehta tha : usey mujh se door rakho, aur wo kehti thi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : an-qareeb ghilaaf hua karengey."
5451,Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur ye izafa kya : to main usey (iske haal par) chhod deta.
5452,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : aik bistar mard ke liye hai aik uski biwi ke liye tesraa bistar mehman ke liye aur chotha bistar shaitan ke liye hai.
5453,"Imam Malik ne Naafe , Abdullah-bin-Dinar aur Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat ki, un sab ne unhein Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs takabbur se kapda ghaseet kar chaley Allah Taala uski taraf nazar tak nahi karega."
5454,"Ubaidullah , Ayub , Lais-bin-Sad aur Usama un sab ne Naafe se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya : qiyamat ke din ( nazar nahi karega .)"
5455,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne apne walid Salim bin-Abdullah aur Naafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs takabbur se kapda ghaseet kar chalta hai qiyamat ke din Allah Taala uski taraf nazar nahi farmaeyga ."
5456,"Maharib bin Disaar aur jabla bin Suhem ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sab ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5457,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hanzala ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Salim se unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki : kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne takabbur se kapda ghaseeta Allah Taala qiyamat ke din uski taraf nazar tak nahi farmaeyga."
5458,"Ishaq bin Sulaiman ne kaha : hamein Hanzala bin abi Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Salim se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they usi ki tarah magar unhon-ne ( kapda ghaseetaa ke bajaey) kapdey (ghaseetey) kaha."
5459,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Muslim-bin-Yunaaq se suna, wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne aik shakhs ko chadar ghaseet kar chaltey huey dekha unhon-ne us se puchha : tum kis qabeeley se ho? us ne nasb bataya wo shakhs banu- Leis se tha, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko pehchan liya aur kaha : maine apne un donon kanon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke aap farma rahe they. jis shakhs ne apni izaar (kamar se nichey ki chadar wghaira) ghaseeti us se iska irada takabbur ke siwa aur na tha to qiyamat ke din Allah Taala uski taraf nazar tak nahi farmaeyga."
5460,"Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman abu Yunus aur Ibrahim bin Naafe un sab ne Muslim-bin Yunaaq se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki magar abu Yunus ki hadis mein hai : abul-Hasan Muslim se riwayat hai aur un sab ki riwayat mein hai, jisne apni izaar ghaseeti unhon-ne apna kapda nahi kaha."
5461,"hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Ibad bin Jafar se suna, keh rahe they : maine Naafe bin abd al-Haaris ke ghulam Muslim-bin Yasar se kaha ke wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal karein kaha : aur main un donon ke darmyan betha tha (unhon-ne sawal kya : ( kya aap ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us shakhs ke barey mein koi baat suni jo takabbur se apni izaar ghaseet-ta hai? unhon-ne kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna tha : qiyamat ke din Allah Taala uski taraf nazar tak nahi farmaeyga ."
5462,"Abdullah-bin Waqid ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se guzra meri kamar ki chadar kisi had tak latak rahi thi to aap ne farmaya Abdullah ! apni chadar uper kar lo. maine apni chadar uper kar li. aap ne farmaya : aur zyada kar lo maine aur zyada uper ki, phir main usko uper karta raha yahan tak ke kuchh logon ne kaha kahan tak ( uper karey) ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pindliyon ke aadhey hisson tak."
5463,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aur unhon-ne aik shakhs ko chadar ghaseet kar chaltey huey dekha us shakhs ne zamin par paon mar maar kehna shuru kar diya : ameer aagey ameer aa gaey. wo (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) Bahrain ke ameer they. (ye dekh kar Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha jo shakhs itraatey huey zamin par apni izaar ghaseet-ta hai Allah Taala uski taraf nazar tak na farmaeyga ."
5464,"Muhammad-bin Bashshaar ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki. aur ibne- Musanna ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi Adi ne hadis sunai, un donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, ibne- Jafar ki riwayat mein hai : Marwan Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni ghair haziri mein Madina ka (qaaim maqam) Hakim banaya karta tha aur ibne- Musanna ki hadis mein hai : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko (hakim ki ghair-haziri mein) Madina ka Hakim banaya jata tha."
5465,"Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin ziyad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aap ne farmaya : aik shakhs apne baalon aur apni chaadaron par itraata hua chal raha tha ke achcha usko zamin mein dhansa diya gaya aur wo qiyamat tak zamin mein dhansta chala jaeyga."
5466,"Shoba ne hamein Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
5467,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs akadta hua apni 2 chaadaron mein chala ja raha tha, apne aap par itraa raha tha Allah Taala ne usey zamin mein dhansa diya wo qiyamat tak zamin mein dhansta chala jaeyga."
5468,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se khabar di kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein sunain, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadison sunain, unmein se (eik ( ye thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs 2 chaadaron mein itraata hua ja raha tha phir usi ki tarah bayan kya."
5469,"abu Raafe ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. tum se pahley ki aik ummat mein aik shakhs chaadaron ke aik jodey mein itraata hua ja raha tha phir un sab ki hadis ki tarah zikr kya."
5470,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne nazar bin Anas se, unhon-ne Bashir bin Nuhaik se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne soney ki anguthi (pahnney, istemal karne) se mana farmaya."
5471,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis sunai aur ibne- Musanna ki hadis mein hai, kaha : maine nazar bin Anas se suna."
5472,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Kureb ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ke hath (ki ungli) mein soney ki anguthi dekhi, aap ne usko utaar kar phenk diya aur farmaya tum mein se koi shakhs aag ka angaara uthata hai aur usey apne hath mein daal leta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tashrif ley janey ke baad us shakhs se kaha gaya : apni anguthi ley lo aur us se koi fayda utha lo. usne kaha : Allah ki qasam! main usey kabhi nahi uthaunga. jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey phenk diya hai."
5473,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi Muhammad-bin Rumeh aur Quteba ne kaha : hamein Leis ne Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki aik anguthi banwaai aap usey pahntey to uska nageena hatheli ke andar ki taraf kar liya kartey they, to logon ne bhi soney ki anguthiyan banwaa lein, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif farma huey. us anguthi ko utaar diya aur farmaya : main us anguthi ko pehnta tha to nageeney ko andar ki taraf kar leta tha. phir aap ne usey phenk diya aur farmaya : Allah ki qasam! main usko kabhi nahi pahnunga. phir logon ne bhi apni apni anguthiyan phenk din. hadis ke alfaz Yahya ke) bayan ki hui ( hain."
5474,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr Yahya-bin-Saeed Khalid-bin Haris aur Aqba bin Khalid sab ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se soney ki anguthi ke barey mein hadis riwayat ki, Aqba bin Khalid ki riwayat main (Ubaidullah ne) ye izafa kya : aur aap ne usey daain hath mein pehna."
5475,"Ayub Musa-bin-Aqba aur Usama sab ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se soney ki anguthi ke barey mein Leis ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
5476,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki aik anguthi banwaai, pehley wo aap ke hath mein thi phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein rahi phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein rahi phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein rahi yahan tak ke wo un (hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) se arees ke kuwein mein gir gaee, us (anguthi) par Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naqsh tha. ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai : yahan tak ke wo aik kuwein mein gir gaee, unhon-ne ye nahi kaha : unse ( gir gaee. ("
5477,"Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki aik anguthi banwaai, phir aap ne usko phenk diya, iske baad aap ne chandi ki aik anguthi banwaai, usmein ye naqsh karaya : Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur farmaya : koi shakhs meri us anguthi ke naqsh ke mutabiq naqsh na banwaaey . jab aap us anguthi ko pahntey to anguthi ke nageeney (motey chaudey hissey) ko hatheli ke andar ki taraf kar liya kartey they aur yahi wo anguthi thi jo Mueqeeb (ke hath ( se chaah arees mein gir gaee thi."
5478,"Hammad ne hamein Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki aik anguthi banwaai, usmein Muhammad Rasulullah naqsh karaya aur logon se farmaya : maine chandi ki aik anguthi banai hai aur is mein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naqsh karaya hai, so koi shakhs us naqsh ke mutabiq naqsh kanda na karaaey."
5479,"Ismail (ibne-Ulaih) ne Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur is mein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( naqsh karaaney (ka zikr nahi kya."
5480,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Qatada ko Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Rome (mojooda Itly) (ke badshah) ki taraf khat likhney ka irada kya to sahaba ne kaha : wo log koi aisa khat nahi padhtey jis par mehar na lagai gaee ho, kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki aik anguthi ki banwaai, aisa lagta hai ke main ab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hathon mein uski safedi ko dekh raha hun, is par Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naqsh hai."
5481,"Muaz bin Hisham ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahale-ajam ki taraf khat likhney ka irada kya to aap se puchha gaya ke wo log sirf us khat ko qabool kartey hain jis par mehar lagi ho, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki aik anguthi banwaai. kaha : mujhey aisa lagta hai ke main (ab bhi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein us (anguthi) ki safedi ko dekh raha hun."
5482,"Khalid-bin Qais ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kisraa , qaisar aur Najashi ki taraf khat likhney ka irada farmaya to aap se puchha gaya ke wo log sirf us khat ko qabool kartey hain jis par mehar lagi ho, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mehar dhalwaai, wo chandi ki anguthi thi aur is mein Muhammad Rasulullah naqsh karaya."
5483,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bin Malik se riwayat ki aik unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein chandi ki aik anguthi dekhi, phir logon ne bhi chandi ki anguthiyan banwaaein aur pahan lin, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni anguthi phenk di to logon ne bhi apni anguthiyan phenk din."
5484,"Rooh ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Ziyad ne bataya ke ibne-Shahab ne unhein khabar di, Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unhon-ne aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein chandi ki aik anguthi dekhi, phir sab logon ne chandi ki anguthiyan dhalwaain aur pehan lin, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni anguthi phenk di to logon ne bhi apni apni anguthiyan phenk din."
5485,abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5486,"Abdullah-bin Wahab misri ne kaha : mujhey Yunus bin Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki anguthi chandi ki thi aur uska nagina habsh ka tha."
5487,"Talha bin Yahya Ansari ne Yunus se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne daaein hath mein chandi ki aik anguthi pahni, usmein habsh ka nagina tha, aap iske naginey ko hatheli ki taraf rakha kartey they."
5488,Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Yunus bin Yazeed se isi sanad ke sath Talha bin Yahya ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya.
5489,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki anguthi us ungli mein thi, ye keh kar unhon-ne baaein hath ki chhanguli ki taraf ishara kya."
5490,"ibne-Idrees ne kaha : maine Aasim bin Kulaib se suna, unhon-ne abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aap yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey us ungli ya uske paas wali ungli mein anguthi pahnney se mana farmaya, Aasim ko ye yad nahi raha ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kon-si 2 ungliyon mein (pahnney se mana kya tha). padhi. aur aap ne mujhey qass ke reshami kapdey pahnney aur reshami gaddon par baithney se mana farmaya, unhon-ne (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha qassi (reshami) dhaariyon wala kapda Misr aur Sham (Syria) se aata tha, usmein kuchh shabeehein (tasweeron jaisey naqsh w nigaar ( hoti hain. aur Mayasir usko kehtey hain jo auratein apne khaawindon ki khaatir zeen par rakhney ke liye banati thin, jis tarah arghuani rang ke gaddey hon."
5491,"Sufiyan ne Aasim bin Kulaib se, unhon-ne abu-Musa ( Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) ke aik betey se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
5492,"Shoba ne Aasim bin Kulaib se riwayat ki, kaha : maine abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mana farmaya, ya mujhey mana farmaya, unki murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se thi (iske baad) isi tarah bayan kya."
5493,"abu-Ahwas ne Aasim bin Kulaib se, unhon-ne abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya tha ke main un donon mein se kisi ungli mein anguthi pehnun, phir unhon-ne darmyani aur (angoothey ki taraf se) uske sath wali ungli ki taraf ishara kya."
5494,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine aik ghazwey ke doran mein, jo ham ne lada, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : kasarat se (aksar oqaat) jootey pehna karo, kyonke aadmi jab tak jootey pahan kar rakhta hai sawar hota hai. (uske paon isi tarah mehfooz rahtey hain jis tarah sawar ke aur wo sawar hi ki tarah tezi se chal sakta hai.)"
5495,Muhammad-bin-Ziyad ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs jootaa pahney to daain ( paon ( se shuru karey aur jab jootaa utaarey to baain ( paon ( se ibtida karey aur donon jootey pahney ya donon jootey utaar de.
5496,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs aik jootey mein na chaley, donon jootey pahney ya donon jootey utaar de."
5497,"ibne-Idrees ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Rizeen se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaey, unhon-ne apni peshani par hath mar kar farmaya : suno ! kya tum is tarah ki baatein kartey ho ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf baatein mansub karta hun. taake tum hidayat pa jao aur main khud gumrah ho jaun, sun lo ! main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ke jootey ka tasma toot jaey to wo usko theek karne se pahley doosrey ( jootey ( mein na chaley."
5498,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu-Rizeen aur Abu-Saleh se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke ham mana riwayat ki."
5499,"Malik-bin-Anas ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke aadmi apne baain hath se khaaey, ya aik joota pehan kar chaley aur aisa kapda pahney jis mein bahar nikalney waley aaza (sar, hath, paon) ke liye suraakh na hon aur aik hi kapda is tarah kamar aur ghutnon ke gird baandhey ke uski sharmgah zahir ho."
5500,"abu khaisma ( Zuhair ( ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ya unhon ne kaha :). maine ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab tum mein se kisi ka tasma toot jaey. ya (farmaya ( jis shakhs ke jootey ka tasma toot jaey. to wo aik (hi) jootey mein na chaley. yahan tak ke apna tasma theek kar ley, aik mozey mein bhi na chaley, apne baain hath se na khaaey, na (ukdoon baith kar) iklautey kapdey ko kamar aur ghutnon ke gird baandhey, na hath paon band kar deney wala libaas pahney."
5501,"Leis ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath paon wghaira ko band kar deney wala libaas pahnney , aik kapdey se kamar aur ghutnon ko baandhney aur chit let kar aik paon ko doosrey ke uper (rakhtey huey usko) uthaney se mana farmaya."
5502,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik joota pehan kar na chalo aur aik chadar (ho to us) ko ghutney khadey karke unke aur kamar ke gird na baandho, baaein hath se na khaao, hath paon band kar deney wala kapda na pehno aur jab chit letey ho to aik taang ko dusri taang ( khadi karke us ( par na rakho ."
5503,"Ubaidullah bin Akhnas ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs chit let kar apni taang ko dusri taang ( khadi karke us ( par na rakhey."
5504,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ibad bin Tameem se, unhon-ne apne chacha ( Abdullaah-bin-Zaid-bin-Aasim Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein us haalat mein chit letey huey dekha ke aap ne ( donon taangein zamin par bichhaaey huey) aik paon doosrey paon par rakha hua tha."
5505,"ibne-Uena, Yunus aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
5506,"Yahya-bin-Yahya , abu Rabe aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki. Yahya ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur doosrey donon ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zafrani rang (se rangey kapdey pahnney) se mana farmaya, Quteba ne kaha ke Hammad ne kaha : yani mardon ko (mana farmaya)"
5507,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne hamein Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mard ko zafraani rang ( pahnney ( se mana farmaya,"
5508,"abu-Khaisma ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : fateh Makka ke saal ya fateh Makka ke din Hazrat abu-Qahafa (Raziallahu anhu) ko laya gaya, wo aaey aur unke sar aur dadhi ke baal Saghaam ya saghaama (ke safaid phoolon ( ki tarah they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar ki aurton ko hukm diya, ya unke barey mein (unke ghar ki aurton ko) hukm diya gaya, farmaya is ( safedi) ko kisi cheez (aur rang ( se badal dein."
5509,"ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : fateh Makka ke din Hazrat abu-Qahaafa (Raziallahu anhu) ko laya gaya, unke sar aur dadhi ke baal safedi mein saghaama (ke safaid phoolon ( ki tarah they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ( safedi ( ko kisi cheez se tabdeel kar do aur siyah rang se ijtinab karo."
5510,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahood aur aur nasara (baalon ko) rang nahi lagaatey tum unki mukhalifat karo (baalon ko rang lagaao.)
5511,"Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim ne apne walid se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wada kya ke wo aik khas ghadi mein unke paas aaeingey, chunanche wo ghadi aa gaee lekin Jibreel (Alaihissalam) na aaey. (us waqt) aap ke hath mein aik asaa tha. aap ne usey apne hath se ( nichey ( phenka aur farmaya : na Allah Taala apne waadey ki khilaf warzi karta hai na rasool (khilaf warzi kartey hain.) Jibreel ameen (Alaihissalam) bhi wahi lekar anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki taraf aaney waley Allah ke rasool they) phir aap ne dhyaan diya to aik char paai ke nichey kuttey ka aik pilla tha. aap ne farmaya : Aaisha ! ye kutta yahan Kab ghusa? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey bilkul pata nahi chala. aap ne hukm diya to us (pilley ( ko nikal diya gaya, phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) tashrif ley aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aap ne mere sath wada kya tha mein aap ki khaatir betha raha lekin aap nahi aaey. unhon-ne kaha aap ke ghar mein jo kutta tha, mujhey us ne rok liya ham aisey ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jis mein kutta ho. na (us mein jahan) tasweer ho."
5512,hamein Wahab ne isi sanad ke sath abu-Hazim se hadis sunai ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wada kya ke wo aap ke paas aaeingey phir hadis bayan ki aur abu-Hazim ke betey ki tarah lambi tafseel nahi batai .
5513,"Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey bataya ke aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fikr mandi ki haalat mein subah ki. Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! main aaj din (ke shuruat) se aap ki haalat mamool (routine) ke khilaf dekh rahi hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ne mujh se wada kya tha ke aaj raat mujh se milengey lekin wo nahi miley. baat ye hai ke unhon-ne kabhi mujh se wada khilaafi nahi ki, kaha : to us roz pura din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kaifiyat yahi rahi phir unke dil mein kuttey ke aik pilley ka khayal baith gaya. jo hamarey (eik bistar ke nichey bin janey waale) aik kheme (numa hissey) mein tha. aap ne uske barey mein hukm diya to usey nikal diya gaya, phir aap ne apne hath se pani liya aur us jagah par chhidak diya. jab Sham hui to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) aa kar aap se miley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : aap ne mujh se wada kya tha ke aap mujhey kal raat milengey? unhon-ne kaha haan bilkul , lekin ham aisey ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jis mein kutta ya tasweer ho. phir jab subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( aawaara ya bekar) kutton ko maar dene ka hukm diya, yahan tak ke aap baagh ya khet ke chhotey kuttey ko bhi (jo rakhwali nahi kar sakta) maarney ka hukm de rahe they aur baagh khet ke badey kuttey ko chhod rahe they. (aisey kuttey gharon se bahar hi rahtey hain aur waqei rakhwaali ki zarurat poori kartey hain.)"
5514,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jis mein kutta hona (is ghar mein jis mein) koi tasweer ho."
5515,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Utba se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap farma rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : Farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jismein kutta ho na (us ghar mein jismein) koi tasweer ho."
5516,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath Yunus ki hadis ki tarah aur sanad mein khabar dene ki wazahat kartey huey riwayat ki.
5517,"Leis ne hamein Bukair se hadis sunai unhon-ne basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin-Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jismein koi tasweer ho. Basar ne kaha : phir iske baad Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey. ham unki iyaadat ke liye gaey to (dekha) unke darwazey par aik parda tha jismein tasweer (bani hui) thi maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke le-paalak Ubaidullah Kholani se kaha : kya Hazrat Zaid ne pehley din (jab mulaqat hui thi.) hamein tasweer (ki manaahi) ke barey mein khabar (hadis) bayan nahi ki thi? to Ubaidullah ne kaha : jab unhon-ne kapdey par baney huey naqsh ke siwa ke alfaz kahey they, to kya tum ne nahi suney they?"
5518,"mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne khabar di ke unhein Bukair-bin-Ashajj ne hadis sunai, unhein Basar-bin-Saeed ne hadis sunai ke Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis sunai aur (is waqt) Basar ke sath Ubaidullah Kholani they. (kaha (Hazrat abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein ye hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jis mein tasweer ho. Basar ne kaha : phir Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey, ham unki iyaadat ke liye gaey to ham ne unke ghar mein aik parda dekha jis mein tasweerein thin maine Ubaidullah Kholani se kaha : kya (Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid ne) hamein tasaaweer ke mutaalliq hadis bayan nahi ki thi? (Ubaidullah ne) kaha : unhon-ne (sath hi ye) kaha tha : siwaey kapdey ke naqsh ke kya aap ne nahi suna tha maine kaha : nahi unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi! unhon-ne uska zikr kya tha."
5519,"banu-Najjaar ke aazad karda ghulam abu hubaab Saeed bin Yasar ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they us ghar mein Farishtey dakhil nahi hotey jis mein kutta ho, na (is mein jahan ( mujassamey hon."
5520,"(Saeed bin Yasar ne) kaha : (ye hadis sun kar) main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya aur kaha : unhon ( abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ghar mein Farishtey dakhil nahi hotey jis mein kutta ho. na (us mein) jahan kisi tarah ki tasweerein hon. kya aap ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat suni jo unhon-ne bayan ki? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : nahi. (maine is tarah ye alfaz nahi suney) lekin main tumhen wo bataati hun jo maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kartey huey dekha. maine aapko dekha ke aap apne ghazwey mein tashrif le gaey to maine nichey bichhaaney ka aik mota sa kapda liya aur darwazey par uska parda bana diya jab aap aaey aur aap ne wo kapda dekha to maine aap ke chehre anwar par na-pasandidgi ke aasaar mehsus kiye, phir aap ne usey pakad kar kheencha aur usey phaad diya uske (2 tukdey kar diye aur farmaya : Allah ne hamein pattharon aur mitti ko kapdey pahnaaney ka hukm nahi diya. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : phir ham ne us kapdey mein se do takiye (banaaney ke liye 2 tukdey) kaat liye aur maine un donon ke andar khajooron ki chhaal bhar di. aap ne iske sabab se mujh par koi eitiraz nahi farmaya."
5521,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Dawud se, unhon-ne azra se, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Sad bin Hisham se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : hamarey yahan aik parda tha jis mein parindey ki tasweer thi, jab koi shakhs andar aata ye tasweer iske samney aa jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya is pardey ko hata 2 kyonke main jab bhi andar aata hun aur us pardey ko dekhta hun to duniya ko yad karta hun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : hamarey paas aik chadar thi, ham kehtey they ke uske kinaron par silaa hua kapda resham hai, ham us chadar ko pahntey they."
5522,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : hamein ibne-abi Adi aur Abdul-Aala ne isi sanad ke sath ( Dawud se) hadis bayan ki, ibne- Musanna ne kaha : aur is mein unhon-ne. unki murad Abdul-Aala se hai. ye izafa kya : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein us chadar ko kaatney ka hukm nahi diya."
5523,"abu-Usama ne Hisham (bin Urwa) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar se wapas aaey, maine ro'eindaar kapda darwazey ka parda banaya hua tha jis par paron waley ghodon ki tasweerein thin to aap ne mujhey (utaarne ka ( hukm diya to maine usko utaar diya."
5524,"Abda aur Wakee ne isi sanad ke sath hamein (Hisham-bin-Urwa se) hadis bayan ki, Abda ki hadis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar se aaey ke alfaz nahi hain."
5525,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey aur maine aik motey se kapdey ka parda latkaaya hua tha, is par tasweer thi to aap ke chehre anwar ka rang badal gaya. phir aap ne parde ko pakda aur phaad diya, phir farmaya : qiyamat ke din shadeed tareen azab mein padey huey logon mein se wo (bhi) hongey jo Allah Taala ki paida ki hui (jaandaar) cheezon ke jaisi (mushabeh (similar)) banaaney ki koshish kartey hain."
5526,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan tashrif laaey, (aagey usi tarah) jis tarah Ibrahim bin Sad ki hadis hai, albatta unhon-ne kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us (pardey) ki taraf lapkey aur apne hath se usko phaad diya."
5527,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, un donon ki hadis mein hai : logon mein se shadeed tareen azab mein padey huey (wo log hongey) unhon-ne main se ke alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
5528,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo keh rahi thin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey aur maine apne taaq par mota sa kapdey ka parda latkaaya hua tha jismein tasweerein thin. jab aap ne uske pardey ko dekha to usko phaad daala aap ke chehre anwar ka rang badal gaya aur aap ne farmaya : Aaisha ! qiyamat ke din Allah Taala ke nazdeek sabse shadeed azab ke mustahiq wo log hongey jo Allah Taala ki takhleeq ki mushabihat (similarity) karengey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ham ne us pardey ko kaat diya aur us se aik ya 2 takiye bana liye (eik ya 2 ke barey mein shak rawi ki taraf se hai.)"
5529,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qasim se suna, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke unke paas aik kapda tha jis mein tasweerein thin, wo taaq par latkaa hua tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us taraf rukh karke Namaz padha kartey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usko mujh se hata do. to maine usko hata diya aur uskey takiye bana liye."
5530,Saeed bin Aamir aur abu-Aamir aqadi ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
5531,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laaey, aur maine aik bichhaaney waley kapdey ka parda banaya hua tha, usmein tasweerein thin, aap ne usko hatwa diya aur maine us se 2 takiye bana liye."
5532,"Bukair ne kaha : Abdur-Rehman bin-Qasim ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhein unke walid ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne aik parda latka rakha tha jis mein tasaaweer thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey to aap ne us pardey ko utaar diya, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine usko kaat kar do takiye bana liye, (jab ye hadis bayan ki ja rahi thi) to us majlis mein aik shakhs ne, jo Rabee bin Ata kahlaatey they, banu-zohra ke Maula they, kaha : kya aap ne abu-Muhammad (Qasim-bin-Muhammad) ko ye bayan kartey huey suna ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un donon ( takyon (ke sath tek lagaatey they? to ( Abdur-Rehman ( ibne-Qasim ne kaha : nahi, usne kaha : lekin maine yaqinan (unse) ye baat suni thi. unki murad (unke walid) Qasim-bin-Muhammad se thi."
5533,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne aik (chhota sa, baithney ke liye) gaddaa khareeda jis mein tasweerein bani hui thin, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ( gaddey ( ko dekha to aap darwazey par thahar gaey aur andar dakhil na huey, maine aap ke chehrey par na-pasandidgi ke aasaar mehsus kiye, (ya kaha :) aap ke chehrey par na-pasandidgi ke aasaar mehsus huey, to unhon (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! main (sachey dil se) Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney tauba karti hun. maine kya gunah kya hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye gaddaa kaisa hai? unhon-ne kaha : maine ye aap ke liye khareeda hai. taake aap is par baithein aur tek lagaaein . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un tasweeron (ke banaaney ( walon ko qiyamat ke din azab diya jaeyga aur unse kaha jaeyga : tum ne jo ( sooratein ( takhleeq ki hain, unko zinda karo. phir farmaya : jis ghar mein tasweerein hon unmein Farishtey dakhil nahi hotey ."
5534,"Quteba aur ibne- Rumeh ne Leis se hadis bayan ki, Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Saqafi ne khabar di, kaha : hamein Ayub ne hadis bayan ki, Abdul-Waris bin Abdus-Samad ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne mere dada ke waastey se Ayub se hadis bayan ki, Haaroon-bin-Saeed eili ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Usama-bin-Zaid ne khabar di, Abu-Bakar Ishaq ne kaha : hamein abu-Salma Khuzai ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein maajishoon ke bhatijey Abdul-Azeez ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se khabar di, un sab ( Lais-bin-Sad , Ayub , Usama-bin-Zaid aur Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ( ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Qasim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ye hadis riwayat ki, unmein se kuchh ki hadis kuchh ki nisbat zyada mukammal hai aur) abu-Salma Khuzai ne) ibne- maajishoon ke bhatijey se riwayat ki hui hadis mein ye izafa kya : unhon (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne farmaya : maine us gaddey ko lekar iske 2 takiye bana liye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein unke sath tek lagaatey they."
5535,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo log tasweerein banatey hain unhein qiyamat ke din azab diya jaeyga, unse kaha jaeyga jinko tum ne takhleeq kya ( ab unko zinda karo.)"
5536,"Ayub ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, usi hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, jis tarah Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki."
5537,"Usman bin abi Sheba ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, abu-Saeed ashajj ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu zuhaa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Masruq se unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan qiyamat ke din sabse zyada azab main (giraftaar) tasweer banaaney waley hongey. ashajj ne yaqinan (ka lafz) bayan nahi kya."
5538,"Yahya-bin-Yahya abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib sab ne abu-Muawiya se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki, ( abu-Muawiya aur Sufiyan ( donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, abu-Muawiya se Yahya aur abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai, qiyamat ke din sabse zyada azab paaney walon mein se tasweer banaaney waley hain. aur Sufiyan ki hadis Wakee ki hadis ki tarah hai."
5539,"Mansoor ne Muslim-bin sabeeh (abu zuha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Masruq ke sath aik makkaan mein tha jismein Hazrat Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki tasaweerein thin (ya mujassamey they) Masruq ne kaha : ye Kisraa ki tasweerein hain? maine kaha : nahi ye Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki tasweerein hain. Masruq ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din sabse zyada azab tasweerein (ya mujassamey) banaaney walon ko hoga."
5540,"Imam Muslim ne kaha : maine Nasar bin Ali jahazmi ke sath Abdul-Aala bin Abdul-Aala se hadis padhi ke hamein Yahya bin abi Ishaq ne (Hazrat Hasan Basri ke bhai) Saeed bin abu Hasan se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : aik shakhs Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya usne kaha : main ye (jaandaaron ki) tasweerein banata hun, aap mujhey unke mutaalliq fatwa dein. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere qareeb aao wo qareeb hua unhon-ne phir farmaya mere qareeb aao wo ( mazeed qareeb aaya aap ne iske sar par hath rakh kar farmaya : main tum ko wo baat bataata hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : har tasweer banaaney wala jahannam mein hoga aur uski banai hui tasweer ke badley mein Allah Taala aik jaandaar banaeyga wo usey jahannam mein azab dega aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar tum ne zaroor ( yahi kaam ( karna hai to darakhton ki aur jin chizon mein jaan nahi unki tasweer banao. Nasar bin Ali ne (jab maine unke samney ye hadis padhi ( uska iqrar kya (ke unhon-ne Abdul-Aala bin Abdul-Aala se isi tarah riwayat ki.)"
5541,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne nazar bin Anas-bin-Malik se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha, aap ne (poochhney walon ke mutaalbey par) fatwey dene shuru kiye aur ye nahi keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah farmaya hai yahan tak ke aik shakhs ne unse sawal kya ke main ye tasweerein banata hun, Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : qareeb aao. wo shakhs qareeb aaya Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. jis shakhs ne duniya mein koi tasweer banai usko is baat ka mukallaf banaya jaeyga ke wo qiyamat ke din usmein Rooh phoonkey aur wo usmein Rooh nahi phoonk sakega."
5542,Qatada ne nazar bin Anas se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik shakhs aaya aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
5543,"ibne-Fuzail ne Umara se, unhon-ne abu-Zura se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Marwan ke ghar gaya, unhon-ne us ghar mein tasweerein dekhin to kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya us shakhs se bada zaalim kon hoga jo meri makhlooq ki tarah makhlooq banaaney chala ho. wo aik zarra to banaein ya aik daana to banaein ya aik jo to banaein!"
5544,"Jarir ne Umara se, unhon-ne abu-Zura se riwayat ki, kaha : main aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Madina mein aik ghar mein gaey jo Saeed ( ibne- Aas ( (Raziallahu anhu) ya Marwan (ibne-Hakam) ke liye banaya ja raha tha, wahan unhon-ne aik musawwir ko ghar mein tasweer banatey huey dekha, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur) Jarir ne) ya aik jau to banaaein (ke alfaz ( bayan nahi kiye."
5545,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ghar mein Farishtey dakhil nahi hotey jis mein mujassamey (but) ya tasweerein hon."
5546,"Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Suhel ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (rehmat ke) Farishtey (safar) un rafeeqon ke sath nahi chaltey jinke darmyan kutta ho aur na (unke sath jinke paas) ghanti ho."
5547,Jarir aur Abdul-Azeez darawardi donon ne Sehal se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
5548,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghanti shaitan ki baansuri hai.
5549,"Imam Malik ne Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr se, unhon-ne Ibad bin Tameem se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abu Bashir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke wo aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik qaasid ko bheja. Abdullah-bin Abu-Bakar ne kaha : mera guman hai ke unhon-ne kaha : log apni apni soney ki jagah mein pahunch chukey they. (aur hukm diya) : kisi oont ki gardan mein taant (kamaan ke donon sirey jodey ne wali mazbut baareek chamdey ki dori) ka haar. ya koi bhi haar. na chhod aa jaey magar usey kaat diya jaey. Imam Malik ne farmaya : mera khayal hai ke ye ( haar ( nazar bad se bachaney ke liye ( galey mein daley jatey ( they."
5550,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke) janwar ko) munh par maara jaey ya munh par nishani sabt ki jaey."
5551,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne ibne-Juraij se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke) janwar ko) munh par maara jaey ya munh par nishani sabt ki jaey."
5552,"Hajjaj-bin Muhammad aur Muhammad-bin-Bakr donon ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, pichhli hadis ki tarah."
5553,"Hajjaj-bin Muhammad aur Muhammad-bin-Bakr donon ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, pichhli hadis ki tarah."
5554,Maaqil ne Abu-Hurera se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se aik gadha guzra jiske munh par daagha gaya tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne usey (munh par) daagha hai is par Allah ki laanat ho.
5555,Maaqil ne Abu-Hurera se unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se aik gadha guzra jiske munh par daagha gaya tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne usey (munh par) daagha hai is par Allah ki laanat ho.
5556,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam naaim abu Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik gadha dekha jiske chehrey ko nishani lagaaney ke liye daagha gaya tha aap ne usko bahut bura khayal kya, unhon-ne (Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main jo hissey chehrey se sabse zyada door ho iske ilawa kisi jagah nishani sabt nahi karta. phir unhon-ne apne gadhey ke barey mein hukm diya to uski peeth (ke wo hissey jahan dam hilatey waqt lagti hai) par nishani sabt ki gaee ye pahley aadmi hain jinhoney us jagah daaghney ka shuruat kya."
5557,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam naaim abu Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik gadha dekha jiske chehrey ko nishani lagaaney ke liye daagha gaya tha aap ne usko bahut bura khayal kya, unhon-ne (Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main jo hissey chehrey se sabse zyada door ho iske ilawa kisi jagah nishani sabt nahi karta. phir unhon-ne apne gadhey ke barey mein hukm diya to uski peeth (ke wo hissey jahan dam hilatey waqt lagti hai) par nishani sabt ki gaee ye pahley aadmi hain jinhoney us jagah daaghney ka shuruat kya."
5558,"Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bachcha paida hua to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : Anas! us bachchey ka dhyan rakho, uske munh mein koi cheez na jaey yahan tak ke subah tum usko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley jao aap usey ghati dengey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke main subah ke waqt aaya, us waqt aap baagh mein they, aap ke jism par aik kaley rang ki banu-jon ki banai hui naqshdar ooni chadar thi aur aap un sawari ke janwaron (ke jism) par nishan sabt farma rahe they jo fateh Makka ke zamaney mein (fatah Makka ke fauran baad jange-Hunain ke mauqe par) aapko hasil huey they."
5559,"Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin ( ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bachcha paida hua to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : Anas! us bachchey ka dhyan rakho, uske munh mein koi cheez na jaey yahan tak ke subah tum usko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley jao aap usey ghati dengey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke main subah ke waqt aaya, us waqt aap baagh mein they, aap ke jism par aik kaley rang ki banu-jon ki banai hui naqshdar ooni chadar thi aur aap un sawari ke janwaron (ke jism) par nishan sabt farma rahe they jo fateh Makka ke zamaney mein (fatah Makka ke fauran baad jange-Hunain ke mauqe par) aapko hasil huey they."
5560,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hadis bayan kartey huey suna, ke jab unke walid ke yahan bachcha paida hua to wo log us bachchey ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey taake aap usey ghutti dein us waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) oonton ke aik baadey mein they aur bakriyon ko nishan laga rahe they Shoba ne kaha : mera ghalib guman ye hai ke unhon-ne (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha tha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) un ( bakriyon (ke kanon par nishan laga rahe they. (oonton ko lagaaney ke baad bakriyon ko bhi wahin la kar nishan laga rahe they. ("
5561,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hisham bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hadis bayan kartey huey suna, ke jab unke walid ke yahan bachcha paida hua to wo log us bachchey ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas le gaey taake aap usey ghutti dein us waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) oonton ke aik baadey mein they aur bakriyon ko nishan laga rahe they Shoba ne kaha : mera ghalib guman ye hai ke unhon-ne (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha tha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) un ( bakriyon (ke kanon par nishan laga rahe they. (oonton ko lagaaney ke baad bakriyon ko bhi wahin la kar nishan laga rahe they. ("
5562,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hisham bin Zaid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas oonton ke baadey mein gaey, us waqt aap bakriyon ko nishan laga rahe they ( , Shoba ne) kaha : mera khayal hai) Hisham ne) kaha : ke un ( bakriyon (ke kanon par) nishan laga rahe they. ("
5563,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Shoba se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hisham bin Zaid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas oonton ke baadey mein gaey, us waqt aap bakriyon ko nishan laga rahe they ( , Shoba ne) kaha : mera khayal hai) Hisham ne) kaha : ke un ( bakriyon (ke kanon par) nishan laga rahe they. ("
5564,"Khalid-bin Haris , Muhammad ( ibne- Jafar ghandar ( , Yahya (bin Saeed qattaan (aur Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ( sab ne Shoba se, isi sanad se, usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
5565,"Khalid-bin Haris , Muhammad ( ibne- Jafar ghandar ( , Yahya (bin Saeed qattaan (aur Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi ( sab ne Shoba se, isi sanad se, usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
5566,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein nishan lagaaney wala aala dekha, aap sadqey mein aaey huey oonton par nishan sabt farma rahe they."
5567,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein nishan lagaaney wala aala dekha, aap sadqey mein aaey huey oonton par nishan sabt farma rahe they."
5568,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Umar-bin Naafe ne apne walid se khabar di. unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaza se mana farmaya, maine Naafe se puchha : qaza kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : bachchey ke sar ke kuchh hissey ke baal moond diye jayen aur kuchh hissey ko chhod diya jaey."
5569,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Umar-bin Naafe ne apne walid se khabar di. unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaza se mana farmaya, maine Naafe se puchha : qaza kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : bachchey ke sar ke kuchh hissey ke baal moond diye jayen aur kuchh hissey ko chhod diya jaey."
5570,"abu-Usama aur Abdullah-bin-Numair donon ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur unhon-ne abu-Usama ki hadis main (qaza ki) tafseer ko Ubaidullah ka qaul qarar diya hai. (unke shagirdon ke samney Ubaidullah ne ye wazaahat Naafe ki taraf mansub kiye baghair bayan ki.)"
5571,"abu-Usama aur Abdullah-bin-Numair donon ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur unhon-ne abu-Usama ki hadis main (qaza ki) tafseer ko Ubaidullah ka qaul qarar diya hai. (unke shagirdon ke samney Ubaidullah ne ye wazaahat Naafe ki taraf mansub kiye baghair bayan ki.)"
5572,Usman bin Usman ghatfaani aur Rooh ( bin-Qasim ( ne Umar-bin Naafe se Ubaidullah ki sanad se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur donon ne tafseer (qaza ki wazaahat ( ko hadis ka la hiqa banaya. ( alag se bayan nahi kya. (
5573,Usman bin Usman ghatfaani aur Rooh ( bin-Qasim ( ne Umar-bin Naafe se Ubaidullah ki sanad se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur donon ne tafseer (qaza ki wazaahat ( ko hadis ka la hiqa banaya. ( alag se bayan nahi kya. (
5574,"Ayub aur Abdur-Rehman siraaj ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki."
5575,"Ayub aur Abdur-Rehman siraaj ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki."
5576,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raston mein baithney se bacho . logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamarey liye apni majlison mein baithey baghair chaara nahi wahin ham aik doosrey se guftgu kartey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum baithey baghair nahi reh saktey to rastey ka ( jahan majlis hai) haq ada karo. logon ne puchha : rastey ka haq kya hai? aap ne farmaya : nigaahein jhuka kar rakhna (chalney walon ke liye) takleef ka sabab banney wali chizon ko hataana salam ka jawab dena, achi baat ka hukm dena aur burai se rokna."
5577,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raston mein baithney se bacho . logon ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamarey liye apni majlison mein baithey baghair chaara nahi wahin ham aik doosrey se guftgu kartey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum baithey baghair nahi reh saktey to rastey ka ( jahan majlis hai) haq ada karo. logon ne puchha : rastey ka haq kya hai? aap ne farmaya : nigaahein jhuka kar rakhna (chalney walon ke liye) takleef ka sabab banney wali chizon ko hataana salam ka jawab dena, achi baat ka hukm dena aur burai se rokna."
5578,Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad madni aur Hisham bin Saeed un donon ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5579,Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad madni aur Hisham bin Saeed un donon ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5580,"abu-Muawia ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne Fatima binte-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : meri beti dulhan hai. usey khasra (kuchh riwayat mein chechak) nikla tha to uske baal jhad gaey hain kya main (iske baalon ke saath) doosrey baal jod dun? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ne baal jodney wali aur judwaaney wali (donon) par laanat ki hai."
5581,"abu-Muawia ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne Fatima binte-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : meri beti dulhan hai. usey khasra (kuchh riwayat mein chechak) nikla tha to uske baal jhad gaey hain kya main (iske baalon ke saath) doosrey baal jod dun? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ne baal jodney wali aur judwaaney wali (donon) par laanat ki hai."
5582,"Abdullah-bin-Numair, Abda, Wakee aur Shoba sab ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath abu-Muawiya ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, magar Wakee aur Shoba ne apni riwayat main ( فَتَمَرَّطَ شَعْرُهَا ( (iske baal chhidrey ho gaey hain) ke alfaz kahey."
5583,"Abdullah-bin-Numair, Abda, Wakee aur Shoba sab ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath abu-Muawiya ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki, magar Wakee aur Shoba ne apni riwayat main ( فَتَمَرَّطَ شَعْرُهَا ( (iske baal chhidrey ho gaey hain) ke alfaz kahey."
5584,"Mansoor ki walida ne Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : maine apni beti ki shadi ki hai, uske baal jhad gaey hain, uska shauhar usko khoobsurat dekhna chahta hai, Allah ke rasool! kya main uske baalon ke sath doosrey baal jod dun? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey mana farma diya."
5585,"Mansoor ki walida ne Hazrat Asma binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : maine apni beti ki shadi ki hai, uske baal jhad gaey hain, uska shauhar usko khoobsurat dekhna chahta hai, Allah ke rasool! kya main uske baalon ke sath doosrey baal jod dun? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey mana farma diya."
